English:CategoryHistory


點選下列和歷史、傳統、和回溯相容相關的主題：

* EmacsHistory -- the big picture
* EmacsSchism －－ Emacs 和 XEmacs 的分裂
* DynamicBindingVsLexicalBinding

RichardStallman 寫了一些設計 Emacs 時的備忘錄：
ftp://publications.ai.mit.edu/classic-hits/AIM-519A.ps

JamieZawinski drew up an emacs timeline a couple of years back:
http://www.jwz.org/doc/emacs-timeline.html.

CraigFinseth 在他的網頁上有一些和 Emacs 相關的有趣玩意兒。參閱：
EmacsImplementations for a huge list of Emacs-like editors.

One of the earliest TECO EMACS manuals dated 1982-03-06:
http://zane.brouhaha.com/~healyzh/emacs/emacs.doc.txt

TECO EMACS version 170 from Rich Alderson for the PDP10 emulator is
available here:  http://pdp10.nocrew.org/

Beginning with version 21, Emacs was able to display inline images, so
it was possible to display a splash image when
starting-up. http://www.ee.ryerson.ca/~elf/emacs/logo/ describes the
story behind the creation of the Emacs logo.
